sers can download the Agua app and seamlessly sync it with their radio through Agua\'s listening tech, making it easier than ever to enjoy the benefits of this groundbreaking technology.\n\nExperience the future of radio broadcasting and join the revolution with Agua Technology.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"team-wrap\">\n<div class=\"team-image-block\"><img src=\"http://44.204.173.71/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/WILL-CUNNINGHAM-295x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"295\" height=\"300\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-32\" /></div>\n<div class=\"team-content-block\">\n<h2>Will Cunningham</h2>\n<h3>President &amp; CEO</h3>\nWill brings 20 years of Public and Private Radio experience as well as Commercial Music Industry experience to this dynamic technology. His extensive market study and work with radio, advertising and marketing mediums is what inspired this project. Will had the vision to see this giant gap in technology and access and is why he created the AGUA platform for artists and advertisers digital, by upgrading antiquated Radio spots into an interactive experience.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"team-wrap\">\n<div class=\"team-content-block\">\n<h2>Leila Steinberg</h2>\n<h3>Director of Industry Relations and Key Advisor</h3>\nLeila Steinberg, Music Manager and Founder of Aimfortheheart.org, a non profit organization serving at- risk youth. Tupac\'s manager and mentor. Leila brings her incredible energy, dedication and knowledge of the music industry. She plays a big role as AGUA\'s Key Advisor in the industry for artists and Film/Music industry professionals.\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"team-image-block\"><img src=\"http://44.204.173.71/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/LEILA_STEINBERG-300x221.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"221\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-39\" />\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"team-wrap\">\n<div class=\"team-image-block\"><img src=\"http://44.204.173.71/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/AUGUSTINE_WONG-300x257.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"257\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-34\" /></div>\n<div class=\"team-content-block\">\n<h2>Augustine Wong</h2>\n<h3>CTO</h3>\nAugustine has spent his career focused on launching and managing creative and innovative new products and businesses across various industries with much of it in content, music technology, and analytics. He brings his entrepreneurial spirit and energy to help build a platform that offers the ease of use and dynamic interface to its clients. Augustine brought his engineering and analytics experience to the development of the platform since its inception.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"team-wrap\">\n<div class=\"team-content-block\">\n<h2>Tyler Smith</h2>\n<h3>Silicon Valley Liaison &amp; Global Deal Maker</h3>\nTyler is a global dealmaker, relationship manager and serial entrepreneur. Pangea Force\'s global network is the heart of his organization. Tyler is responsible for maximizing global network utility; ensuring that entrepreneurs, Pangea Force Ambassadors, network family-offices, LPs and partnering corporations connect across borders with the right network nodes based on each of their needs. As Chief of Staff at Pangea Force, Tyler helps to oversee Pangea\'s world-wide operations. Tyler has been Day-One with Will Cunningham\'s Journey of AGUA and has contributed greatly as a mentor and Key Advisor\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"team-image-block\"><img src=\"http://44.204.173.71/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/TYLER_SMITH-300x285.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"285\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-42\" /></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"team-wrap\">\n<div class=\"team-image-block\"><img src=\"http://44.204.173.71/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/ASHER-UNDERWOOD-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-33\" /></div>\n<div class=\"team-content-block\">\n<h2>Asher Underwood</h2>\n<h3>COO/ Marketing &amp; Production</h3>\nAsher is an All-Star at AGUA. His eclectic experience working at a high energy advertising agency specializing in national and regional success. As well as his commercial production experience for TV, radio, film production, and advertising has been essential in developing the tools to best suit AGUA\'s clients needs. Asher has been onboard since the beginning of AGUA, he remains a key team member of AGUA throughout the software development and coding.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"team-wrap\">\n<div class=\"team-content-block\">\n<h2>Ron Weisberg</h2>\n<h3>CCO</h3>\nRon is the owner of Story Quest Studios and Chief Creative Officer at Agua Technology. With over 20 years of experience in film production, he has created numerous short film productions for clients, including award-winning narrative shorts. Ron\'s expertise also includes motion picture production, and he has worked on projects for the UNM Kids Camp program and the Albuquerque Film &amp; Music Experience. Ron\'s extensive experience in film production and creative direction makes him an invaluable member of the Agua Technology team, helping to position the company as a leader in audio recognition and content management.\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"team-image-block\"><img src=\"http://44.204.173.71/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/IMG_4586-200x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"200\" height=\"300\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-36\" /></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"team-wrap\">\n<div class=\"team-image-block\"><img src=\"http://44.204.173.71/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/NORA-JUDITH-WREN-MILTON.heic\" alt=\"\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-40\" /></div>\n<div class=\"team-content-block\">\n<h2>Nora Judith Wren Milton</h2>\n<h3>Executive VP &amp; Creative Director</h3>\nNora Judith Wren Milton is AGUA\'s Executive Vice President and Creative Director. As the creative force behind our user interface, Nora draws on her experience as a songwriter, recording artist, and health/beauty product entrepreneur to bring a unique perspective to our team. With a passion for supporting women-owned small businesses, Nora shares AGUA\'s vision of providing artists and advertisers with a user-friendly platform to access the market. Her innovative ideas and creative vision have been instrumental in AGUA\'s success, and we\'re proud to have her as a key member of our leadership team.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"team-wrap\">\n<div class=\"team-content-block\">\n<h2>Taylor Durant</h2>\n<h3>Board Member/Key Advisor</h3>\nTaylor has been executively producing and advancing this company behind the scenes in ways no other team member has. Agua is so grateful to have Taylor on the board and as a key advisor. Her experience as a Business Owner, Part-time Life Coach, and Angel Investor grants vision to Agua and to the software\'s user experience. She is also certified in Crypto Real Estate.\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"team-image-block\"><img src=\"http://44.204.173.71/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/TAYLOR_DURANT-260x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"260\" height=\"300\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-41\" /></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"team-wrap\">\n<div class=\"team-image-block\"><img src=\"http://44.204.173.71/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/DOMENICK-NATI-300x189.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"189\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-35\" /></div>\n<div class=\"team-content-block\">\n<h2>Domenick Nati</h2>\n<h3>Public Relations</h3>\nKnown as \"The King of Contacts\", Domenick Nati has held successful careers in television/film production, public relations, and mainstream radio. His movie and TV credits include Talladega Nights, Boo! A Madea Halloween, Deal or No Deal, Hells Kitchen, Making the Band, So You Think You Can Dance, and many more. In 2006 he established Nati Celebrity Services, a full-service entertainment public relations agency, he has brought his talents and skills to AGUA.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"team-wrap\">\n<div class=\"team-content-block\">\n<h2>Vincent McDaniel</h2>\n<h3>Chief Connector &amp; Strategic Relationship Manager</h3>\nVincent E. McDaniel is an experienced film and music industry professional who brings a vast network of connections to his role as Chief Connector and Strategic Relationship Manager at Agua Technology. With a background as a television host, actor, stunt performer, and producer, Vincent has a wealth of expertise in the entertainment industry. His insights into how technology can be used to advance the industry, along with his extensive network of industry connections, make him a valuable asset to our organization. In addition to his work at Agua Technology, Vincent\'s company, Dream Team Productions, develops scripts for TV series and feature films.\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"team-image-block\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"team-wrap\">\n<div class=\"team-image-block\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-25\" src=\"http://44.204.173.71/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/istockphoto-1223671392-612x612-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"612\" height=\"612\" /></div>\n<div class=\"team-content-block\">\n<h2>Josh Combs</h2>\n<h3>Token Developer &amp; Brand Ambassador</h3>\nJosh Combs is a dedicated family man, Agua’s original Token Developer and Brand Ambassador. He played a crucial role in developing the Wah Token by utilizing his technical expertise in creating smart contracts. Josh\'s enthusiasm and willingness to help in any way he can has made him the spirit animal of this company, driving the team\'s momentum forward. He also serves as a valuable brand ambassador, promoting Agua Technology\'s mission and values. Josh\'s passion for the industry and dedication to the team have made him an integral part of the Agua Technology family, and his contributions extend beyond his technical expertise.\n\n</div>\n</div>', 'Team', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '14-autosave-v1', '', '', '2023-03-31 14:51:34', '2023-03-31 14:51:34', '', 14, 'http://44.204.173.71/?p=23', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
