 successful careers in television/film production, public relations, and mainstream radio. His movie and TV credits include Talladega Nights, Boo! A Madea Halloween, Deal or No Deal, Hells Kitchen, Making the Band, So You Think You Can Dance, and many more. In 2006 he established Nati Celebrity Services, a full-service entertainment public relations agency, he has brought his talents and skills to AGUA.</p>\r\n	</div>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"team-wrap\">\r\n\r\n	<div class=\"team-content-block\">\r\n		<h2>Vincent McDaniel</h2>\r\n		<h3>Chief Connector & Strategic Relationship Manager</h3>\r\n		<p>Vincent E. McDaniel is an experienced film and music industry professional who brings a vast network of connections to his role as Chief Connector and Strategic Relationship Manager at Agua Technology. With a background as a television host, actor, stunt performer, and producer, Vincent has a wealth of expertise in the entertainment industry. His insights into how technology can be used to advance the industry, along with his extensive network of industry connections, make him a valuable asset to our organization. In addition to his work at Agua Technology, Vincent\'s company, Dream Team Productions, develops scripts for TV series and feature films.</p>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"team-image-block\">\r\n		<img class=\"size-full wp-image-25\" src=\"http://44.204.173.71/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/istockphoto-1223671392-612x612-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"612\" height=\"612\" />\r\n	</div>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"team-wrap\">\r\n\r\n	<div class=\"team-image-block\">\r\n		<img class=\"size-full wp-image-25\" src=\"http://44.204.173.71/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/istockphoto-1223671392-612x612-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"612\" height=\"612\" />\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"team-content-block\">\r\n		<h2>Josh Combs</h2>\r\n		<h3>Token Developer & Brand Ambassador </h3>\r\n		<p>Josh Combs is a dedicated family man, Agua’s original Token Developer and Brand Ambassador. He played a crucial role in developing the Wah Token by utilizing his technical expertise in creating smart contracts. Josh\'s enthusiasm and willingness to help in any way he can has made him the spirit animal of this company, driving the team\'s momentum forward. He also serves as a valuable brand ambassador, promoting Agua Technology\'s mission and values. Josh\'s passion for the industry and dedication to the team have made him an integral part of the Agua Technology family, and his contributions extend beyond his technical expertise.</p>\r\n	</div>\r\n\r\n</div>', 'Team', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '14-revision-v1', '', '', '2023-03-31 10:33:55', '2023-03-31 10:33:55', '', 14, 'http://44.204.173.71/?p=28', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
